):

1. *Njena* kosa je bila svetlo braon. (Her hair was light brown.) 
2. *Kosi* mi je kuću. (He mows my house.) 
3. Ona *koši* travu svaki dan. (She mows the grass every day.) 
4. *Kosom* je obrijala glavu. (She shaved her head with a razor.) 
5. On je *košio* travu u parku. (He was mowing the grass in the park.)